Received this item on time and the english subtitles were great. I had been looking for this movie with english subs and hadn't found it, so happy i was able to buy it here :)
Just love it. I enjoy watching the movie. its so cute and the shipping was fast. I would suggest people to order this it worth the watchning

This is one of my all time favorite movies! Any girl or guy who has experienced their first crush/love will relate to this story line! The main characters really showed great chemistry. I highly recommend this movie. It will especially be great for a girls night out/sleep over! I heard there will be a part two in the works, but nothing official has been confirmed.

My cousin made me watch this movie.  I wish they have this on amazon instant video. Not so thrilled about buying DVD's anymore.  Whenever someone visits they borrow the dvds and don't return it and this is one movie that I love to watch over and over again. ^_^

To anyone in love, this a awesome movie to watch.  Perfect to watch with your friends or that someone you have been crushing on since you can remember. I do not care who you are but if you do not feel any form of emotion watching this, you have no heart!
If you ever had a first love, you can definitely relate to this movie! Don't know how many times I've watched this movie but I know I cried each time. ;')

First of all I will like to thank the seller for offering this item. I saw this movie once fell in love with it and decided to buy it. I had a tough time finding it then I came across this seller. Love the product the conditions were great. And what is even better I got it before I was expecting to get it. :D
